# Icons, actions, and tables (Executiva Cloud)

**Accessible labels** (`aria-label`, `title`) should match the product language (**pt-BR**) where user-facing.

## Global ViewSwitcher (card / list / table)

- The `ViewSwitcher` component lives in the **main app header** (`MainAppLayout.tsx`), next to the executive selector — NOT inside individual views.
- `MainAppLayout` owns a single `layout: LayoutView` state and passes it as a prop to every view.
- Views accept `layout: LayoutView` in their props and render card / list / table accordingly.
- Hidden for `dashboard` and `settings` views (no listing to switch).

## Toolbar layout (per-screen)

- **Row 1 (above search)**: action icons — page-size `<AppSelect>`, CSV `<PrinterIcon>`, Add `<PlusIcon>`, Settings `<CogIcon>` — in a `flex flex-wrap items-center justify-end gap-2` div.
- **Row 2 (below icons)**: search field in a `ToolbarPanel` (e.g. `<AppSearchInput>`).
- **Row 3 (optional)**: filter pills (type, status, priority) in a `ToolbarPanel`.
- Page-size selects use `aria-label="Itens por página"` with **no visible label text**.

## CSV export

- `PrinterIcon` button (`Icons.tsx`) triggers `downloadCsv()` from `utils/csvDownload.ts`.
- Exports **all filtered records** (not just the current page), BOM-prefixed UTF-8.
- File names follow `<entity>_YYYY-MM-DD.csv` pattern.

## Edit / Delete

- Import `typeMgmtEditIconBtn` and `typeMgmtDeleteIconBtn` from `components/ui/typeManagementStyles.ts`.
- Stroke color comes from `EditIcon`/`DeleteIcon` (`Icons.tsx`) via `currentColor`; do not duplicate SVGs with per-screen fixed colors.
- Pattern: `rounded-full`, `text-slate-500`, hover `bg-slate-100` + indigo/red. After standardization, avoid `text-slate-400` + `hover:bg-slate-200` for these pairs unless documented.

## "Actions" column

- `inline-flex flex-row flex-nowrap items-center justify-end`, cell `whitespace-nowrap text-right`, `<th>` `text-right` and `min-w-*` so icons stay on one line.
- Do not add informational columns without sustainable data.

## Domain-specific actions (e.g. Users)

- **Invite**: icon-only `PlusIcon` button with `title="Convidar usuário"` and `aria-label`.
- **Invite / password**: `LockClosedIcon`; explanatory `title`/`aria-label`; loading with `aria-busy` / opacity — do not mimic a generic loader.
- **Deactivate**: `NoSymbolIcon` when the screen uses icon actions.

## Icon-only buttons

- Always `type="button"` outside submit flows, and **`aria-label`** (+ `title` for tooltip when useful).
